Event.Message: DirectWrite has started creating a factory object.
DirectWrite has stopped creating a factory object.

DirectWrite has stopped connecting to the font cache service
DirectWrite has started getting the shared font cache.
DirectWrite has stopped getting the shared font cache.

Event.Message: DirectWrite has added an element to the client-side font cache.
